<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٣٢١٣ - أَخْبَرَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/691">‌إِسْمَاعِيلُ بْنُ مَسْعُودٍ، </a>قَالَ: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1717">‌خَالِدٌ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/729">‌</a><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٥٩⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>أَشْعَثَ ، عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1389">‌الْحَسَنِ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2316">‌سَعْدِ بْنِ هِشَامٍ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3026">‌عَائِشَةَ </a>أَنَّ رَسُولَ اللهِ صَلَّى اللهُ عَلَيْهِ وَسَلَّمَ <span class="c2">«نَهَى عَنِ التَّبَتُّلِ»</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>